<h3>Drop Shipping</h3>

<p>Preferred shipping method: <%= @on_boarding.preferred_shipping_method %></p>

<div>
  <h5>What are your preferred carriers?</h5>
  <% @on_boarding.onboarding_carriers.each do |v| %>
      <p>- <%= v.name %></p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<p>What is your protocol for freight shipments? <%= @on_boarding.protocol_for_freight_shipments %></p>

<h3>Warehousing</h3>

<p>Do you have ship alone items? <%= @on_boarding.ship_alone_items %></p>

<div>
  <h5>Product Type(s):</h5>
  <% @on_boarding.onboarding_product_types.each do |p| %>
      <p> <%= p.name %></p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<p>What are your average inventory levels? <%= @on_boarding.average_inventory_levels %></p>
<div>
  <p>What is your typical shipping lead time?</p>
  <%= @on_boarding.typical_shipping_lead_time_count %>
  <%= @on_boarding.typical_shipping_lead_time_day %>
</div>

<div>
  <p>What are your average inventory replenishment timelines?</p>
  <%= @on_boarding.average_inventory_replenishment_time_count %>
  <%= @on_boarding.average_inventory_replenishment_time_day %>
  <% unless @on_boarding.average_inventory_replenishment_time_other.blank? %>
      <p>Other: <%= @on_boarding.average_inventory_replenishment_time_other %></p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<h3>Product Details</h3>

<h5>How and when do you provide inventory updates (including discounted and new items)?</h5>

<div>
  <p>Method: <%= @on_boarding.method %></p>
  <% unless @on_boarding.method_other.blank? %>
      <p>Other: <%= @on_boarding.method_other %></p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div>
  <p>Frequency: <%= @on_boarding.frequency %></p>
  <% unless @on_boarding.frequency_other.blank? %>
      <p>Other: <%= @on_boarding.frequency_other %></p>
  <% end %>
</div>
<p>Are there any costs/fees in addition to COGs? <%= @on_boarding.costs_fees_radio %></p>
<% unless @on_boarding.if_so_costs_fees.blank? %>
    <p>If so, how are these costs billed? <%= @on_boarding.if_so_costs_fees %></p>
<% end %>

<p>Are there any special requirements:<%= @on_boarding.requirements_for_purchase_orders %></p>
<% unless @on_boarding.if_yes_requirements_for_purchase_orders.blank? %>
    <p>If yes, please explain the requirements:  <%= @on_boarding.if_yes_requirements_for_purchase_orders %></p>
<% end %>

<% unless @on_boarding.imap_pricing.blank? %>
    <p>Please explain your discount/promotional rules in regards to IMAP pricing:<%= @on_boarding.imap_pricing %></p>
<% end %>

<p>What, if any, are your merchandising stipulations and strategy recommendations for your
  product?<%= @on_boarding.merchandising %></p>

